      <description>&lt;p&gt;I have extensive experience as a teaching assistant and professional tutor in mathematics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;teaching-assistant--columbia-university-new-york-ny&#34;&gt;Teaching Assistant — Columbia University (New York, NY)&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Differential Geometry&lt;/strong&gt; - Fall 2022&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Intro to Higher Mathematics&lt;/strong&gt; - Fall 2023 and 2024&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Calculus I&lt;/strong&gt; — Spring 2023 and 2025&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Calculus II&lt;/strong&gt; — Spring 2024&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Responsibilities included leading discussion sections, holding office hours, grading assignments and exams, and providing individual student support.&lt;/p&gt;
